%N A395707 Expansion of g^7*(5*g-4)/(6-5*g)^4, where g = 1+x*g^6 is the g.f. of A002295.
%F A395707 a(n) = (n+1) * A386368(n+1).
%F A395707 G.f.: (Sum_{k>=0} (5*k+2)/(3*k+2) * binomial(6*k+4,k) * x^k) * (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(6*k,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395707 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k^2 = (1/6) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(6*k,k) * x^k ).
%F A395707 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(6*k+4+l,k) * binomial(6*n-6*k-l,n-k) for every real number l.
%F A395707 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 5^(n-k) * binomial(6*n+5,k).
%F A395707 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 6^(n-k) * binomial(5*n+k+4,k).
%o A395707 (PARI) a(n) = (n+1)*sum(k=0, n, 5^(n-k)*binomial(6*n+5, k));
